00:46:14,887 --> 00:46:17,848
[SPEAKER_09]: I disagree with that as a blanket exemption.

514
00:46:19,228 --> 00:46:31,551
[SPEAKER_09]: I think that the environmental benefits of the photovoltaic array need to be properly weighed against the loss of ecosystem services and benefits on a case-by-case basis.

515
