553
00:50:21,200 --> 00:50:29,202
[SPEAKER_13]: We have to say that there are certain places in and around Medford that could certainly have more trees

554
00:50:30,675 --> 00:50:34,458
[SPEAKER_13]: It could be the cemetery, it could be any number of places.

555
00:50:35,679 --> 00:50:55,497
[SPEAKER_13]: I think we would be remiss if we don't require the city of Medford to keep track of open spaces that can have more trees planted so that when people have to mitigate and pay fees and so forth,

556
00:50:55,863 --> 00:50:58,825
[SPEAKER_13]: We don't start running around looking for a place to put a tree.

557
00:50:59,265 --> 00:51:09,570
