561
00:51:29,738 --> 00:51:32,239
[SPEAKER_00]: Lois, is there some reason why you think we don't?

562
00:51:32,359 --> 00:51:39,021
[SPEAKER_00]: Because the city, for example, planted 200 trees between September and the start of December this year.

563
00:51:39,041 --> 00:51:46,864
