571
00:52:22,652 --> 00:52:33,894
[SPEAKER_13]: Well, no matter what, it should be spelled out somewhere that the tree warden has a register of places that can take trees.

572
00:52:34,834 --> 00:52:36,474
[SPEAKER_13]: It shouldn't look random.

573
00:52:36,834 --> 00:52:38,135
[SPEAKER_13]: It should look planned.

