01:24:34,735 --> 01:24:37,756
[SPEAKER_10]: Loretta, I would recommend that we propose it.

890
01:24:39,016 --> 01:24:45,498
[SPEAKER_10]: I think it's worth a discussion like why did the building inspector, that was in there at one point in the draft.

