[SPEAKER_10]: It was discussed at the council, I believe, as you know, would have to register as well as get a permit for tree removal.

896
01:25:07,087 --> 01:25:09,707
[SPEAKER_10]: And I think it's a good idea.

897
01:25:10,028 --> 01:25:17,850
[SPEAKER_10]: There may be counter arguments to it that we ought to hear, but I think putting it out there at least puts it on the table for discussion.

898
01:25:18,831 --> 01:25:24,092
