01:25:27,113 --> 01:25:30,134
[SPEAKER_14]: I mean that's what this is about is that our response to comments.

901
01:25:31,094 --> 01:25:38,316
[SPEAKER_14]: And trees meant for this as their work we can also support that but we can add additional comments to their consideration.

902
01:25:40,736 --> 01:25:43,157
[SPEAKER_07]: We need to bring this discussion to a close but I guess.

903
01:25:43,617 --> 01:25:44,257
[SPEAKER_07]: Thanks.

